              "messages": {
                "default": [
                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we're learning how to handle objections at work.\nSometimes people disagree or raise concerns.\nLet's learn how to respond politely and professionally!",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/83a19357-0a16-423a-a89c-9de8ff842c4c-Objection-Handling---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "When someone shares a concern, you can say:\n\"I understand your concern about [issue].\"\nFor example: \"I understand your concern about the pricing.\"\nThis shows you are listening to them.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/83a19357-0a16-423a-a89c-9de8ff842c4c-Objection-Handling---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Tell me more!",
                    "text": "When someone makes a good point, you can say:\n\"That's a fair point. Let me explain why we [action].\"\nFor example: \"That's a fair point. Let me explain why we picked this tool.\"\nThis shows respect before you give your reason.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/83a19357-0a16-423a-a89c-9de8ff842c4c-Objection-Handling---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Cool!",
                    "text": "You can also thank someone for their feedback:\n\"Thanks for raising this. [Reason it matters].\"\nFor example: \"Thanks for raising this. Timelines are important for your launch.\"\nThis makes the other person feel valued.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/83a19357-0a16-423a-a89c-9de8ff842c4c-Objection-Handling---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Start Practice!",
                    "text": "Now let's practice handling objections!",
                    "media": {
